Rating: 4
Double Yum!! I've made this for years and always get raves.The crust is fantastic. Though I've made the sauce with rhubarb and love it, I've also used mixed berries (strawberries, blackberries, cherries) along with the vanilla bean. To lighten up the tartness of some lemon sorbets, I mix half sorbet and half vanilla ice cream--it's creamier and still has that nice lemon bite.

